# Bootstrap three-layer boundary — IDE anti-drift contract

**Canonical decision:** [ADR-0035](docs/decisions/0035-three-layer-surface-ide-anti-drift.md) (AGENTS.md **PRIORITY #2**) · Layer 1 seal: [`app/(main)/[locale]/bootstrap/_SEAL.md`](../../app/(main)/[locale]/bootstrap/_SEAL.md)

**If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md` and fix this rule in the same PR.**

Post-login **first-run** and **org dispatcher** use **one product name: `bootstrap`**.

| URL | Layer 2 page | Role |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `/bootstrap` | `BootstrapSetupPage` | 0-org invites + create org |
| `/o` | `OrgDispatchPage` | Org resolution + inline multi-org picker |

**Retired:** `/console` — no redirects, no `lib/features/console/`, no `components2/console/`.

Mechanical guard: [`tests/unit/bootstrap-surface-contract.test.ts`](tests/unit/bootstrap-surface-contract.test.ts)

---

## Prime directive

```txt
Layer 1 — app/           → URL + thin re-exports ONLY
Layer 2 — lib/features/  → dispatch, metadata, fetch, RSC orchestrators (compose only)
Layer 3 — components2/   → shells, picker JSX, client forms (paint only)
```

**Import doors:**

| Layer | Door |
| --- | --- |
| Layer 2 | `#features/bootstrap` · `#features/bootstrap/server` |
| Layer 3 | `#components2/bootstrap` |

Session reverify is **not** bootstrap — use `iam-profile/reverify` + `components2/auth/step-up-reverify-shell.tsx` ([`iam-profile-directory.mdc`](iam-profile-directory.mdc)).

---

## Layer 1 — `app/.../bootstrap/` and `app/.../o/page.tsx`

**Allowed in `page.tsx`:**

```tsx
export {
  generateBootstrapMetadata as generateMetadata,
  BootstrapSetupPage as default,
} from "#features/bootstrap/server"

export { OrgDispatchPage as default } from "#features/bootstrap/server"
```

**Forbidden in Layer 1:**

| Action | Why |
| --- | --- |
| `resolvePostLoginOrgDispatch`, redirects, org lists | Layer 2 |
| `#components2/bootstrap` imports | Layer 3 via Layer 2 only |
| Recreate `/console` or `lib/features/console/` | Retired |

---

## Layer 2 — `lib/features/bootstrap/`

**Owns:** `post-login-org-dispatch.server.ts`, metadata, deferred shell, page orchestrators.

**Allowed module root:** `actions/` · `data/` · `components/` · `schemas/` · `index.ts` · `server.ts` · `client.ts` · `types.ts` · `constants.ts` · `*.contract.ts` · `README.md`

**Forbidden at `lib/features/bootstrap/` root:** `_SEAL.md`

**Orchestrator rule:** Layer 2 pages fetch, redirect, and pass serializable props into Layer 3 — **no** `#components2/ui/*`, **no** `#components2/afenda-brand`, **no** layout JSX beyond composition.

---

## Layer 3 — `components2/bootstrap/`

| File | Role |
| --- | --- |
| `bootstrap-first-run-shell.tsx` | 0-org page chrome |
| `org-dispatch-picker.tsx` | Multi-org picker on `/o` |
| `bootstrap-pending-invites.tsx` | Invite list presentation |
| `bootstrap-create-org-form.client.tsx` | Create-org form |
| `bootstrap-loading.tsx` | Route loading skeleton |

**May import:** `#components2/ui/*`, `#features/org-admin/client` (picker form action only).

**Forbidden:** fetch graphs, `redirect()`, `resolvePostLoginOrgDispatch`.

---

